✓ merge step > calls worktreeManager.mergeWorktree with correct args\n56\t✓ merge step > fails when mergeWorktree returns success: false with conflict\n57\t✓ merge step > fails when mergeWorktree returns success: false with tests-failed\n58\t✓ merge step > worktree cleanup happens via mergeWorktree (not separately)\n59\t```\n60\t\n61\t## AC 5: validate step calls validateMerge from cross-worktree-validator.ts\n62\t\n63\t```bash\n64\tnpx vitest run --reporter=verbose src/lib/__tests__/epic-flow-executor.test.ts 2>&1 | grep 'validate step'\n65\t```\n66\t\n67\t```output\n68\t✓ validate step > calls validateMerge with correct args\n69\t✓ validate step > fails when validation returns valid: false\n70\t```\n71\t\n72\t## AC 6: Epic state transitions at each step boundary\n73\t\n74\t```bash\n75\tnpx vitest run --reporter=verbose src/lib/__tests__/epic-flow-executor.test.ts 2>&1 | grep 'state transition'\n76\t```\n77\t\n78\t```output\n79\t✓ state transitions > transitions completing → merging before merge step\n80\t✓ state transitions > transitions merging → validating before validate step\n81\t✓ state transitions > transitions to done after all steps succeed\n82\t✓ state transitions > does not transition state for retro step (no mapping)\n83\t```\n84\t\n85\t## AC 7: Step failure skips remaining steps and transitions to failed\n86\t\n87\t```bash\n88\tnpx vitest run --reporter=verbose src/lib/__tests__/epic-flow-executor.test.ts 2>&1 | grep 'failure handling'\n89\t```\n90\t\n91\t```output\n92\t✓ failure handling > skips remaining steps on failure\n93\t✓ failure handling > transitions to failed on step failure\n94\t✓ failure handling > handles unknown step name as failure\n95\t✓ failure handling > handles non-Error throw from a step (string coercion)\n96\t✓ failure handling > includes \"unknown\" reason when merge fails without a reason field\n97\t✓ failure handling > handles dispatchRetro throwing an error\n98\t```\n99\t\n100\t## AC 8: EpicFlowResult includes all required fie